title: Loudness - Classic Loudness Live 2009 Japan Tour (Disc2)
description:
Much-anticipated live DVD release from Japanese metal band LOUDNESS! This double live DVD rcontains footage from the band's "CLASSIC LOUDNESS LIVE 2009 JAPAN TOUR " performances. Disc 1 includes a concert at Shibuya Club Quattro on April 12, 2009 and at Ebisu Liqudroom on June 26, 2009. Disc 2 includes a concert on September 5, 2009 at Nakano Sun Plaza.
